      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my super reliable daily driver and has been really well-loved\u2014honestly, it still runs like a dream and looks great inside and out! It\u2019s got so much life left in it and is totally ready for your next road trip or daily commute. I've stayed on top of all the care it needs, so you can just hop in and enjoy the ride. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
